Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好大一张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱的臭狗狗们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…食堂在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,狮子？你是狮子吗
